lead_paragraph: Darrell Dickey was fired yesterday with North Texas (2-7) already assured its second consecutive losing season since winning four Sun Belt Conference titles in a row. Athletic Director Rick Villarreal said Dickey, who has three years left on his contract, would not return in 2007. Dickey is expected to coach the final three games of the season.
